{"tid":523980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警炒車後妻涉頂包 兩人被控妨礙司法公正今提堂","createTime":"2018-01-09T06:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T07:53:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49f8179000069205c225e44f539b9f2f59a194f9","tid":523980,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"休班警於去年7月25日駕駛私家車，駛至黃大仙龍翔道東行時疑失控撞石壆，事後其疑向警方報稱自己是當時的司機，惟意外過程被現場的車CAM拍下，揭發疑有人頂包。夫婦被控妨礙司法公正，案件今提堂，辯方申請兩人押後答辯，以候辯方取進一步法律意見及取得法律文件。<br />\n<br />\n被告為警員張振豪（37歲）及文員李瑩瑩(37歲)，張被控一項不小心駕駛罪，另與李共同被控一項作出傾向並意圖妨礙司法公正罪。案件押後至2月7日再訊，期間兩人獲准繼續以200元及2000元保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57684887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57684887&d=xX77hroXdMzR4jOVmCMNZdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d893717e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57684887&h=090737cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57684887</a>"},{"pid":"2df3671fb71263df555fdc64e4f406e3a9578fc1","tid":523980,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b37c440e74d8591440aa331d84401a0fd721a308","tid":523980,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"而家周街天眼 啲車又裝哂cam<br />\n咁樣都頂包搏蒙就抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dfc57f08110bdfc09197e6ca36392ff33b7bfd","tid":523980,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:38:38.000Z","msg":"作出傾向並意圖妨礙司法公正罪?<br />\n<br />\n意圖咋咩?"},{"pid":"73b517f72714a8d5f9a1014b08ce0f09fdc011d7","tid":523980,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"差人做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/no